snippet.title: F3 2018 - Super Mario 64 Peach's Memory Demo Trailer
snippet.description:
The trailer for my SM64 hack, Super Mario 64 Peach's Memory, at Kaze Emanuar's Fangame E3 2018. Hope you're looking forward to it!

Download: https://drive.google.com/file/d/1eNGOsvbq7w2sKL0_BM8uAyin-DGLQVDT/view?usp=sharing 
How to patch BPS: https://youtu.be/dDNMz2SyGtY 
How to set up the emulator (ft. 12 year old me): https://youtu.be/4BtpkZ1tkXE
